4 5 6

7 Employees in management positions include all managers with disciplinary responsibility.

5.2 Diversity, Equity & Inclusion

→ Global Leadership of Women@Technology & Innovation (GLOW@TI)1: The GLOW@TI network aims to promote careers for women with a background in science. Women in this network are often appointed to technology field and research group management positions.

→ GROW2GLOW1: The GROW2GLOW network provides business coaching for women as a way of helping them realize their full potential. The network comprises more than 140 coaches in 13 countries.